{"tid":961654,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"碧X清潔服務有限公司，男員工欺凌毆打女員工","createTime":"2018-12-30T09:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T12:06:39.000Z","uid":123787,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4ea67eb86a8b855e902bcbca28032d1fadde8ac","tid":961654,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T09:49:31.000Z","msg":"碧X清潔服務有限公司，位於油塘將軍澳墳場工程，男員工 欺凌毆打女員工，事後已報警處理。但警員提意和解，而公司亦包庇男員工，亦因女員工吾識字，碧X公司要她簽下一份離職通知書，而女員工在沒了解通知書內容的情況下簽了，簽後才知道被炒。在影片可見，男員工怎樣欺凌女寡婦。碧X公司亦因此事告訴女員工這不算工傷也沒有賠償。但影片亦可見女員工是在工作範圍被打而受傷，住院4天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157373870477668&amp;id=740472667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157373870477668%26id%3D740472667&d=y7SzFf8rwXZQ0WRSkoCQ%2B%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=89c1bd3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157373870477668&amp;id=740472667</a>"},{"pid":"de114ec3cb50025e0a854081d46f40a8b4103bf3","tid":961654,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"有無來龍去脈 點解會嘈起上黎"},{"pid":"15933e7e8da1a663aec90d0d04e87c477e3081e6","tid":961654,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"最憎人出手<br />\n除非佢世界第一好打<br />\n到下次遇到個勁過佢既人<br />\n佢又比人禁住砌<br />\n打來打去為咩"},{"pid":"4f86fb410e2b957d2f7fecf16ae6e8188f480102","tid":961654,"uid":155431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7ca661db04625b57d81fe72d3979042d0b8cf0","tid":961654,"uid":123787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"每日黎150件<br />\n就係黎片中呢啲大陸人。廣東話都唔識，只係亂咁鳩叫鄉下話，同埋返工打人既人。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係講明話喺油塘，我仲以為條片係大陸拍"},{"pid":"5898cab344090c13715f5a94deb2d12d45ade713","tid":961654,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim